    "name": "NVIDIA NIM Image Generation API",
    "description": "Visual generative AI endpoints. Text-to-image, image-to-image, and image editing using models such as Black Forest Labs FLUX.1, Stable Diffusion XL, Shutterstock-trained Edify Image, and NVIDIA Edify 3D \u2014 exposed by per-model NIM containers with a uniform JSON contract that returns base64-encoded PNG or JPEG artifacts.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: NVIDIA Developer Support",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "createdAt": "2026-06-05T15:13:29.000Z",
